Package com.force.sdk.jpa.table

Class Summary
ColumnImpl Representation of a Force.com field.
ForceColumnMetaData Metadata for fields on Force.com objects.
ForceMetaData Base class for the metadata of objects and fields that will be registered and optionally passed to the schema writer.
ForceTableMetaData Metadata for Force.com objects.
RelationshipImpl Representation of a collection of related objects on a Force.com object.
TableImpl Represents an object (custom or standard) in Force.com.
TableName Force.com objects have names that consist of a namespace, the base name of the object, and a suffix (like __c).
 

Enum Summary
TableName.Type Enum of all possible table types.
